{
  "id": "adv_event_2202_01_04",
  "title": "未来のために",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After a few days",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……こころ、今日も全然姿を見てないわ\nここ最近、部屋にこもりきりよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Kokoro‚ I haven't seen her at all today.\nLately‚ she's been locked up in her room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "endTime": 8.5533335685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、愛はこころとあの日、話したんだよね\nなんて言ってたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ did you talk to Kokoro that day‚ Ai?\nWhat did she say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7400002162,
      "endTime": 14.084966437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、私、聞いてみたんです\nどうしてそんなに思い詰めてるのって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I tried asking her\nwhy she's so obsessed and troubled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2916331609,
      "endTime": 22.0582998593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……話せない、話したくないって……\n私、こころの親友だと思ってたのに……情けなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… she couldn't talk‚ didn't want to…\nI thought I was her best friend… I feel pathetic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.244966507,
      "endTime": 35.2383001329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに辛そうなのに……\n力になってあげられないのが悔しいです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though she looks so tormented…\nIt frustrates me that I can't help her…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4249666851,
      "endTime": 42.8649665516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "そう……。やっぱり、葵の予想通りなのかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Maybe Aoi's prediction was right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0782999993,
      "endTime": 48.044966507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　お二人は理由を知ってるんですか！？\n教えて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Do you two know the reason!?\nPlease tell me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2382997831,
      "endTime": 53.344966634100004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "……本当は、君達には話さないつもりだったんだけど\n二人を泣かせてしまった以上、そうもいかないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Originally‚ I didn't plan on telling you guys.\nBut since I made you both cry‚ I can't do that anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5316333294,
      "endTime": 63.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "愛は覚えてる？\n莉央と僕が、君達と初めて会った日のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ do you remember?\nThe day Rui‚ I‚ and you first met.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6,
      "endTime": 69.0993431886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、NEXT VENUSグランプリの\nセミファイナル直前に、確かバンプロのロビーで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it was during the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix\nright before the semifinals‚ in the Van Pro lobby…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3,
      "endTime": 76.5366671246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、実は僕、足をねんざしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ that day‚ I sprained my foot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7666666667,
      "endTime": 81.0180953185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai005-01.m4a",
      "text": "……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2,
      "endTime": 82.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "こころが廊下を走って、私にぶつかったでしょう\n葵はその時、私を支えてくれたわ。それが原因なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro ran down the hallway and bumped into me‚ right?\nAoi supported me at that time. That's the reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7666666667,
      "endTime": 91.7881869319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ葵さん、怪我をしたままセミファイナルに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Aoi-san participated in the semifinals while injured…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92,
      "endTime": 96.3973243713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "言っておくけど、それは負けた理由じゃないよ\nあの日、僕はベストを尽くせた。そう思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me make it clear‚ that wasn't the reason we lost.\nThat day‚ I did my best. That's what I believe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6,
      "endTime": 104.1361228467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3333333333,
      "endTime": 106.3319954951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "それより、僕は一つミスをしてしまった\nあの日の話をしてるのを、こころに聞かれたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there was one mistake I made.\nKokoro overheard us talking about that day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5333333333,
      "endTime": 113.96811864399999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "この前のライブの後、葵が怪我してると思って\n私があの日の話を蒸し返してしまったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the recent live‚ I thought Aoi was injured‚\nso I brought up that day's conversation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1666666667,
      "endTime": 120.9293427507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "外でこころが聞いているとは思わなくて……\nうかつだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't think Kokoro was listening outside…\nI was careless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1333333333,
      "endTime": 125.8040137015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしてそんな大切なこと\n今まで話してくれなかったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Why didn't you tell us such an important thing\nuntil now!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2666666667,
      "endTime": 132.7920183581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、私達がロビーで騒いだせいで\nそんなご迷惑を掛けていたなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of us making a scene in the lobby‚\ncausing such trouble…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133,
      "endTime": 141.37999984820001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "話したら、そんな風に負い目を感じるからさ\n僕も莉央も、そんなこと望んでない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I told you‚ you would feel guilty like that.\nBoth Rui and I don't want that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.6,
      "endTime": 147.69437598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、こころは聞いてしまったんでしょうね\nだから、責任を強く感じてるんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Kokoro overheard.\nThat's why she feels a strong sense of responsibility.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9,
      "endTime": 155.352742998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "こころが愛に話をしないのは\n愛にまで責任を感じてほしくないからじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe Kokoro doesn't want Ai to feel responsible either.\nShe doesn't want you to feel burdened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.5666666667,
      "endTime": 162.1774138531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……こころ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4,
      "endTime": 165.7239908695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、葵。私達がこころに伝えるべきじゃない？\n私も葵も気にしてないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Aoi. Shouldn't we tell Kokoro?\nBoth you and I aren't concerned about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9,
      "endTime": 173.041700073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだね。愛、それでいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah. Ai‚ is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.2333333333,
      "endTime": 176.8966439088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "……待って下さい\nもう一度チャンスをもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Please wait.\nCan we have another chance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.1,
      "endTime": 182.6010196805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "どうして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.8,
      "endTime": 183.7999999881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
