      "text": "……なんで、愛が泣いてるの？\nおバカな上に泣き虫なんて……おかしいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why is Ai crying?\nCrying like a foolish crybaby… it's strange…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 337.1666666667,
      "endTime": 347.2950979904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
