      "text": "ねえ、こころ……これからは二人で\n……ううん、四人で頑張ろうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kokoro… From now on‚ let's\n…No‚ let's do our best together with the four of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.5,
      "endTime": 357.86040385909996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_04-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "一人で悩まないで\nアイドルを続けるのが無理だなんて、言わないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't bear it alone.\nDon't say that being an idol is impossible.",
