      "text": "過ぎたことを、一人で悔やむんじゃなくて\n未来のことを、みんなで話し合おうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead of regretting what's already happened alone‚\nLet's talk about the future together with everyone.",
        "id": ""
